GNU xorriso
BSD Make (installed as 'bmake'.) This is NOT compatible with GNU Make.
LLVM/Clang
YASM
Rust Cargo-xbuild
Nightly Rust compiler

For testing
_______________
QEMU (KVM optional, use qemu-nokvm instead if not on Linux)


___
Getting Started:

pacman -S rustup
pacman -S clang
pacman -S lld
pacman -S xorriso

cargo install cargo-xbuild
